library(broom)
model_fit_func <- function(df_x1, df_x2, df_x3, data){
  model <- lm(y ~ ns(x1, df = df_x1):ns(x2, df=df_x2):ns(x3, df=df_x3), data = data)
  metrics <- glance(model) %>% mutate(df_1 = df_x1, df_2 = df_x2, df_3 = df_x3)
  return(metrics)
}
